---

## Methods (Plain English)

The EEWS prioritizes **interpretability and robustness** over maximum predictive complexity.

* Feature engineering focused on **temporal stress patterns**, not single events
* Baseline statistical models and interpretable machine learning
* Crossâ€‘county pilot testing to evaluate generalizability

This approach allows nonâ€‘technical stakeholders to understand *why* risk is risingâ€”not just that it is.

